data.description: This one won't last!  Cozy brick ranch in award winning Jenison schools is priced to sell.  The kitchen and dining area features plenty of counterspace, new vinyl flooring and appliances.  Enjoy the warmth of the gas fireplace and fieldstone chimney in the bonus living room.  Downstairs you'll find a 3rd bedroom with egress window, plenty of storage space and area for a rec room.  The large backyard is fully fenced and includes a storage shed.  Open house on Sunday, April 7th 12-2pm.   Hope to see you there!
